      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Correspondence card picturing a wealthier young Muslim couple in traditional dress 'à la turca'. The man is wearing a felt hat (fez) with a scarf wrapped around it, a short sleeveless jacket and a long sleeveless robe (čevkeni). In his left arm he is holding a rapier, a weapon is tucked into his belt and in his right hand he is holding a long pipe (čipuk). The woman is completely veiled. She is wearing a long jacket and a headscarf, which is covering her face.</ab>
